reviews.text: I think it serves the best Siumei in Sai Ying Pun.  However the service is not really up to standard.

This small unassuming place in this quiet neighborhood of Sai Ying Pun is one of my favorite roast meat restaurants in Hong Kong. It was so good I had it twice in my short stay in that area. The roast pork skin was crunchy and the duck meat was so tender. The lady boss is also kindly and spoke to me patiently as I uttered my orders in barely passable Cantonese. No need rush through your meals unlike some places in the city. And if order takeouts, they'd even give you complimentary boxed drinks.
I eat here 3 times a week. Delicious Duel meat lunch offer with rice,  fast service and friendly staff.
One of the tastiest BBQ Pork in HK... the meat melted in mouth... 👍🏼👍🏼
鴨脾飯: 平，靚，正

result.name: 富豪燒臘飯店 Fu Ho Roasted Meat Restaurant

reviews.text:
MTR Sai Ying Pun, gegenüber Ausgang A1
Knusprige Ente, Huhn, Gans, Schweinefleisch und Spanferkel im Fenster. 
Viele Restaurants argumentieren so. Der Gastraum hell, die Einrichtung sauber, gut gelauntes Personal. Das haben schon weniger zu bieten. Die Rezension entsteht nach zwei Besuchen innerhalb von zwei Wochen. 17.00 Uhr und 20.00 Uhr. Von allem Fleisch gekostet: zart und voller Geschmack, die Haut kross und knackig. Die Pfeffer Sauce zur Gans war perfekt. Um 20.00 Uhr hing nicht mehr viel im Fenster. Sauberkeit und gute Laune unverändert. Wir kommen gerne wieder.
